Package au.aklein.metajava

Scan classes for information similar to the reflection API

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Element
    An element which is represented in a class file (either a ClassElement, a MethodElement, a FieldElement or an AnnotationElement
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AnnotationElement
    An object representing an annotation on a type, method or field.
    ClassElement
    An object representing a type Element (class/interface/enum) inside a class file.
    ClassElement.ClassElementBuilder
    Builder class used to construct ClassElement objects from class file data
    FieldElement
    An object representing a field Element from a type or method, inside a class file.
    MetaJava  
    MetaJava.MetaQuery
    Helper class for constructing search queries.
    MetaJava.MetaResult
    Helper class for manipulating results.
    MethodElement
    An element type representing a method contained inside a class.
    ParameterElement
    An object representing a parameter for a MethodElement
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    ElementType
    These constant provide a simple mechanism to specify a certain Element.
